00:44:41.000 --> 00:44:45.000
imagine we are going to treat the
windshield of an automobile.

00:44:45.000 --> 00:44:49.000
So, we want to make it more
resistant to cracking if a stone

00:44:49.000 --> 00:44:53.000
should hit it.
So, this is not to scale,

00:44:53.000 --> 00:44:57.000
of course. This is glass that's
being processed.

00:44:57.000 --> 00:45:01.000
It's in. It's above its softening
point. Rather than just let it cool,

00:45:01.000 --> 00:45:05.000
and cool very slowly,
what we can do is send an air jet

00:45:05.000 --> 00:45:28.760
along the surface.
