00:45:28.760 --> 00:45:32.300
what the air jet will do is cause
the surface to cool more rapidly

00:45:32.300 --> 00:45:35.840
than the center.
We know that glass is a poor

00:45:35.840 --> 00:45:39.380
conductor of heat so we're not going
to expect to this going to be

00:45:39.380 --> 00:45:42.920
isothermal. So,
